
* Create proper working dev environment: Makefile(s), dir structure etc.
* Makefile needs to support:
   - installation of develop/build environment (node.js, npm, docco, cofffeescript, etc)
   - build/cleanup of project
   - running tests
   - generation of docco 
   
* BDD: Specs in Cucumber clone in node.js / tests in Jasmine
* Creation of tests in CoffeeScript
* Implementation of Shelves / Curator in CoffeeScript

